        '<div>former cheerleader, current trophy wife</div>',
        '<div>Few in the high society circles of KC do not know of the Verbecks, who made it big in athletics originally and parlayed it into team ownership. Mr. Ethan Verbeck former NFL player in his 40s, his wife a cheerleader who had the sense to snag him. They have a sixteen year old daughter (Carola) they hope to see as a tennis star, like her maternal aunt (Brandy), who lives with the family. Said sixteen year old daughter has a twin, (Angela) somewhat overlooked for her lack of similar athletic skill. <br><br>In 2022, they were body-jacked by a group of commoner souls, released by Emerson Stodgepole and CC.<br>____________<br>The group''s ringleader, also her legacy likely. Potent in Autumn Arts and a bit of Contract (She is cautious about revealing that). Her own treasure is in fact a contract that can, if need be, allow her influence over her motley, and the ability to spy on them at anytime.</div>'),
